            <description><![CDATA[<pre>Recappi Mini v1.0.104

Cloud polish:
- Refined the Cloud panel toward a more native macOS sidebar/reader feel.
- Kept the account profile fixed at the top of the Cloud sidebar.
- Simplified speaker labels and active states to reduce visual noise.
- Added an inline Sync action to the Cloud audio bar when audio is not local yet.
- Fixed transcript text clicks so they jump to the corresponding audio segment.</pre>]]></description>
